An only-in-Hollywood story about Lionsgate, the Screaming Eagle SPAC, and =
=E2=80=9Ccreditor-on-creditor violence.=E2=80=9D

WILLIAM D. COHAN ( https://puck.news/author/william-cohan/?utm_campaign=3DD=
